<hr style="width:100%", size="3", color=black>  

<h2>Anatomy of an entry</h2>
<p><strong>Phrase:</strong> This is the part that we want the response to</p>
<p><strong>Optional Context:</strong>Context of the situation</p>
<p><strong>Response:</strong> This is the response to the phrase in question</p>

<hr style="width:100%", size="1", color=black>  
<h3>Example:</h3>

<p><strong>Phrase:</strong> How are you?</p>
<p><strong>Optional Context:</strong> I'm a student saying this to a friend</p>
<p><strong>Response:</strong> I'm doing well, and you?</p>

